title: Ebro In The Morning - Independent R&B Star: Muni Long
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Artist & Songwriter Muni Long sits down with Ebro, Laura & Rosenberg to discuss her career journey, some of the struggles she experienced as a songwriter, being independent vs being with a major label & the story behind her hit single 'Hrs and Hrs.'

Watch the video to Hrs and Hrs - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=okfR_VIbXEQ
